Link Protipo Rapido: danydanyestudioafro@gmail.com
4️⃣ Criar o Frontend (React + Vite)

No terminal:

npm create vite@latest frontend

Escolha:

React
JavaScript

Depois entre na pasta:

cd frontend

Instale dependências:

npm install

Instalar Tailwind:

npm install -D tailwindcss postcss autoprefixer
npx tailwindcss init -p

Configure o tailwind.config.js:

content: [
"./index.html",
"./src/**/*.{js,ts,jsx,tsx}",
]

No arquivo index.css:

@tailwind base;
@tailwind components;
@tailwind utilities;
5️⃣ Instalar Supabase no Frontend

Instalar SDK:

npm install @supabase/supabase-js

Criar arquivo:

src/services/supabaseClient.js

Código:

import { createClient } from '@supabase/supabase-js'

const supabaseUrl = 'SUA_URL_SUPABASE'
const supabaseKey = 'SUA_ANON_KEY'

export const supabase = createClient(supabaseUrl, supabaseKey)

Você encontra essas chaves em:

Supabase
→ Project Settings
→ API
